        a
        )
        =
        0
      
    
    {\displaystyle Q'_{x}(b,a)x+Q'_{y}(b,a)y+P_{n-1}(b,a)=0}
  is an asymptote if 
  
    
      
        
          Q
          
            x
          
          ′
        
        (
        b
